-MTpcli73mfiIqW0lpPe.title: Flexbox
-MTpcli73mfiIqW0lpPe.definition: The Flexible Box Module, usually referred to as flexbox, was designed as a one-dimensional layout model, and as a method that could offer space distribution between items in an interface and powerful alignment capabilities

-MTpcliDmrp15A1WIE4U.title: Array.prototype.filter()
-MTpcliDmrp15A1WIE4U.definition: The filter() method creates a new array with all elements that pass the test implemented by the provided function.
